            <p style="font-weight: bold">Client</p>
            <p>A client company that makes use of AMC search facilities.</p>
            <p style="font-weight: bold">Account</p>
            <p>User name and password used by a representative of client companies to log in to HFTools.</p>
            <p style="font-weight: bold">Session</p>
            <p>A session started by the client representative to contain "Runs" of simulations/tests.</p>
            <p style="font-weight: bold">Run</p>
            <p>Simulation/test created by client representative to contain all the "Observations" they made on "Participants".</p>
            <p style="font-weight: bold">Observation</p>
            <p>When client representative observes a "Participant" answering a "Questionnaire" to rate their performance.</p>
            <p style="font-weight: bold">Participant</p>
            <p>Any person that participates in a run (simulation/test) including the client representative that makes observations.</p>
            <p style="font-weight: bold">Questionnaire</p>
            <p>A series of pre determined questions designed to rate the performance of a participant.</p>
